query:
SELECT ar.id, ar.auditInstanceId, ar.auditTemplateQuestionId, ar.response, ar.responseValue, ar.observations, atq.questionText 
FROM auditResponses ar 
JOIN auditTemplateQuestions atq ON ar.auditTemplateQuestionId = atq.id 
WHERE ar.auditInstanceId = 210001 
ORDER BY atq.questionNumber 
LIMIT 10
